Package org.cpnsim.datacenter

Class FailedOutdatedResult<T>

java.lang.Object
org.cpnsim.datacenter.FailedOutdatedResult<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the failed request. It can be Instance or InstanceGroup
public class FailedOutdatedResult<T> extends Object
A class to record the failed requests and the outdated requests. The failed request may need to retry if it has not exceeded the maximum number of retries. The outdated request needs to be marked as failed.
Since:
LGDCloudSim 1.0
Author:
Jiawen Liu
